init_text: An alien has kidnapped Matt Damon, not knowing what lengths humanity goes through to retrieve him whenever he goes missing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien forgot to check if Matt Damon had been in the original movie, The Martian.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The group tracked the alien to a small town in Iowa.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The girls surrounded the alien, and their faces were filled with terror.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They couldn't believe what they were seeing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: This was their idol, their hero.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Matt Damon is a legend, and they had never witnessed him in such a vulnerable position.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien struggled to breathe, but it was futile.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The weight of the girl was too much for it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien was dead and the human girls began their celebration.
